14:38.540 --> 14:41.668
 And I'm not just some girl...
-You've revealed too many details to two

14:41.693 --> 14:43.829
complete strangers
before we've even

14:43.854 --> 14:46.419
asked the questions.
There's no time for this.

14:46.444 --> 14:48.300
We have to get out of here.

14:49.005 --> 14:50.309
- It's okay. it's okay.

14:50.334 --> 14:53.293
It's one of ours.
We've booby-trapped the entire place.

14:55.514 --> 14:56.783
That's not right.

14:58.918 --> 15:03.083
-I suggest whoever is standing
behind that door, you better move

15:03.108 --> 15:05.222
before I blow this door to bits.

15:09.059 --> 15:13.101
-Should we run? Before it?
-No time. Turn over the bed!

15:38.083 --> 15:40.569
-I'm coming in, don't shoot.

15:46.213 --> 15:48.133
Now, get up now.
You're the one who

15:48.158 --> 15:50.558
set up that nice little
kill-zone out there.

