-But now the chemistry lesson is over
and we have real work to do!

35:37.946 --> 35:39.348
-Are there any more?

36:19.457 --> 36:22.277
-It is possible they
killed each other.

36:23.157 --> 36:27.336
The predatory dinosaurs simply
disobeyed the laws of balance.

36:28.506 --> 36:30.002
Just like man.

